MockBot Features:

Modules:
========
Sound
Openni (kinect)
Arduino (servos and analog ports)

http://robotwebtools.org/
MJpegserver and RosBridge
RMS

Hardware:
=========
see SPEC directory

Changes:
Current ATOM CPU is too slow for SLAM and more.
I've changed to Intel NUK i3 CPU, 8GB memory and 64GB SSD
It's amazing !!!

